        // Optionally, add logging:
        // log("Private Sale: Investor sent %amount tokens to %address", _amount, _investor);
    }

    // ... other functions ...
}
```

**2.  Public Launchpad (within the main contract):**

This section will handle the public launchpad.  You'll likely use an oracle for the token price.

```solidity
