If you're building a Docker image from a Dockerfile, place your Dockerfile in the same directory as your Cypress file and adjust the `cypress-docker` configuration accordingly.  For example:

```dockerfile
FROM my-image:latest

WORKDIR /app

COPY package*.json ./
RUN npm install
COPY . .
RUN npm run build # Replace with your build command

